{"id":1009,"date":"2018-09-25T15:28:36","date_gmt":"2018-09-25T08:28:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/?p=1009"},"modified":"2020-07-17T23:15:35","modified_gmt":"2020-07-17T16:15:35","slug":"gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/","title":{"rendered":"Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 &#8211; ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 100k gi\u00fap con ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 sau 1 th\u00e1ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_76 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-6a3c933fc68ca\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-6a3c933fc68ca\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#1_Ly_do_nen_lua_chon_gia_su_Toan_lop_3_tai_nha_cho_con\" >1. L\u00fd do n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 cho con?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#2_Hinh_thuc_gia_su_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_3_tai_nha_o_Ha_Noi\" >2. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#3_Tai_sao_nen_lua_chon_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_3_tai_trung_tam_gia_su_Tri_Viet\" >3. T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#4_Bang_gia_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_3_o_Ha_Noi\" >4. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#5_Cac_con_duoc_doi_ngu_gia_su_Toan_3_giup_do_nhung_gi\" >5. C\u00e1c con \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-gioi-toan-lop-3-chi-tu-100k-giup-con-tien-bo-sau-1-thang\/#6_Luu_y_khi_lua_chon_gia_su_la_giao_vien_hay_sinh_vien_day_kem_mon_toan_lop_3\" >6. L\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-left kksr-valign-top\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;1009&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;0\\\/5 - (0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 - ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 100k gi\u00fap con ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 sau 1 th\u00e1ng&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"5\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-active\" style=\"width: 0px;\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            <span class=\"kksr-muted\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Con gi\u1ecfi To\u00e1n l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng b\u1ed1, b\u00e0 m\u1eb9. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t m\u00f4n To\u00e1n th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c cho con h\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c con tr\u1ebb, gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0 duy To\u00e1n h\u1ecdc <strong>trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong> cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/strong>, <strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong>\u00a0c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1010\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-25-lu\u0301c-4.49.11-CH-300x184.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-25-lu\u0301c-4.49.11-CH-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-25-lu\u0301c-4.49.11-CH.png 674w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Ly_do_nen_lua_chon_gia_su_Toan_lop_3_tai_nha_cho_con\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 120%;\">1. L\u00fd do n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 cho con?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ec3 b\u00e9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp thu.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">V\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng, s\u1edbm ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u00e0 n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng cao<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">R\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, c\u00f3 t\u00ednh k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>==&gt;&gt; Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/strong> c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m <strong>gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ph\u1ee5 huynh trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1012\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/ly-do-nen-thue-gia-su-toan-lop-3-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/ly-do-nen-thue-gia-su-toan-lop-3-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/ly-do-nen-thue-gia-su-toan-lop-3-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/ly-do-nen-thue-gia-su-toan-lop-3-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/ly-do-nen-thue-gia-su-toan-lop-3.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap con n\u1eafm v\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c h\u01a1n!<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Hinh_thuc_gia_su_day_kem_mon_Toan_lop_3_tai_nha_o_Ha_Noi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>2. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">D\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc\u00a0<b>1 gia s\u01b0<\/b>\u00a0\u2013\u00a0<b>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/b>\u00a0gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u00e0i (C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc k\u00e8m nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb 2-5 em h\u1ecdc sinh, t\u1ed1i \u0111a n\u00ean h\u1ecdc 5 h\u1ecdc sinh)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh, tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111i l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u giao th\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 gia s\u01b0 nh\u01b0: Sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, H\u1ecdc kh\u1ed1i ng\u00e0nh, tr\u01b0\u1eddng, qu\u00ea qu\u00e1n, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">L\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc &amp; th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc tu\u1ef3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc: 1,5h &#8211; 2h tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a con, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng h\u1ecdc, tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i th\u00ec h\u1ecdc 2h, n\u1ebfu h\u00f4m n\u00e0o con m\u1ec7t, gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho con h\u1ecdc 1,5h.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1013\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hinh-thuc-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hinh-thuc-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hinh-thuc-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hinh-thuc-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/hinh-thuc-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><em>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc 1 k\u00e8m 1 gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u00e0i h\u01a1n<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Tai_sao_nen_lua_chon_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_3_tai_trung_tam_gia_su_Tri_Viet\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>3. T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">C\u00f9ng hoat \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng trung t\u00e2m <strong>gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong> lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh b\u1edfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh. V\u00ec:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p: Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin &#8212; T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho ph\u1ee5 huynh gia s\u01b0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p &#8212; L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 &amp; b\u00e1o th\u00f4ng tin gia s\u01b0 cho ph\u1ee5 huynh bi\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 cho gia s\u01b0 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho ph\u1ee5 huynh &#8212; Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c &amp; h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn gia s\u01b0 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">M\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 2000+ gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Bang_gia_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_3_o_Ha_Noi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>4. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table width=\"479\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"479\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;  font-size: 120%;\"><strong>H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N TO\u00c1N L\u1edaP 3<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Sinh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">100.000 &#8211; 120.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">200.000 \u2013 250.000<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">150.000 &#8211; 180.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">300.000<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>&gt;= 3 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">==&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <strong>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0<\/strong> t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c update m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2018<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Cac_con_duoc_doi_ngu_gia_su_Toan_3_giup_do_nhung_gi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>5. C\u00e1c con \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em><strong>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/strong> nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u1ecfng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u00a0&#8211; D\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0 duy logic To\u00e1n H\u1ecdc cho c\u00e1c em<em>\u00a0<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em>Nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em>H\u1ecdc ch\u1eafc, nh\u1edb l\u00e2u, t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho nh\u1eefng n\u0103m s\u1eafp t\u1edbi<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em>Lu\u00f4n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em>Lu\u00f4n b\u00e1m s\u00e1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean l\u1edbp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0&#8211;\u00a0<\/em>K\u1ecbp th\u1eddi thay \u0111\u1ed5i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c, c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1028\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/L33-300x102.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/L33-300x102.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/L33-768x262.jpg 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/L33-1024x350.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/L33.jpg 1429w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap con t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Luu_y_khi_lua_chon_gia_su_la_giao_vien_hay_sinh_vien_day_kem_mon_toan_lop_3\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>6. L\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u00a0\u00a0 Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 <strong>k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3<\/strong> l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i b\u0103n kho\u0103n c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 cho phu huynh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em><strong>V\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ea5t g\u1ed1c, h\u1ed5ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c:<\/strong><\/em>\u00a0Con th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o v\u00e0 sinh t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n. Ph\u1ee5 huynh n\u00ean t\u00ecm gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y l\u1edbp 3 cho con b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 con m\u1edbi h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong><em>V\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00e1, gi\u1ecfi:<\/em><\/strong>\u00a0Con \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ph\u1ee5 huynh n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>V\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ea7n \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi<\/strong>: V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, gia \u0111\u00ecnh n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m h\u1ecdc cho con. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u00e9 \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>==&gt;&gt; Tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thu\u00ea sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 cho con m\u00ecnh.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong><em>=&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <\/em><\/strong><em><strong>Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m To\u00e1n + Ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t l\u1edbp 3<\/strong> h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 100k<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <strong>Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u1edbp 3<\/strong> gi\u1ecfi cho con &#8211; Chu\u1ea9n ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p, chu\u1ea9n ph\u00e1t \u00e2m ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong><em>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft, chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao, gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 3 c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng cho ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0 duy To\u00e1n h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><b>TRUNG T\u00c2M<\/b>\u00a0<b>GIA S\u01af<\/b>\u00a0<b>B\u00ccNH MINH<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 : T\u00f2a N03 &#8211; Ph\u1ed1 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, Q.C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p cla